{
  "stem": "24259.1",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The hole was quite small, just about held the four of us.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Certainly you couldn't stand up.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Or if one person turned, I'm told, everybody else had to turn because there was so little room.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And this is the way we hid out for the whole time.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Not the whole time, but we had two other locations after that.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I remember just little things about during the time that we were hiding out.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Occasionally, I would go up to the attic of the barn.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And I remember going up there and seeing a little bit of daylight, because, of course, it was very dark constantly in the-- in the hole.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And that used to be a real treat, getting up there.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And in those days, the farmers used to dry fruits and things in the attic.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And occasionally, I'd find some little things to eat there.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And there was also a time-- this was not very pleasant-- which I remember-- and I'm told I was very good at this-- but I remember, it was-- we had-- what little clothes we had were infested with lice, and that was a time, of course, that I was able to see.",
      "word_count": 52
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And I was very good in finding the lice in-- in the seams, and kind of killing them between my nails.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "That part I remember personally, and so on.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And that used to happen on rare occasions, where I would be able to go out into the attic and see daylight.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was just always very dark, and [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] very cramped, and wet constantly, very moist and so forth.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was just lined with straw and so on.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I just remember I had to be very quiet, of course.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
